<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContentd98484e3acfe49cab755a784416728ee">
</div>
<p>The Ophthalmology Department provides a diagnostic and treatment service for patients with medical eye conditions, including cataracts, glaucoma, squints, eye lid/corneal problems, and eye injuries.</p>
<p>Our consultant team has specialist expertise in oculoplastics, orbit and lacrimal surgery, glaucoma, diabetes, medical retina, neuro ophthalmology and paediatric ophthalmology, and cornea and anterior segment diseases. Â We also provide a an orthoptics service.</p>
<p>The ophthalmology team includes consultants, middle grade doctors, optometrists and orthoptists.</p>
<p>Outpatient clinics are held daily.</p>
<p>You can access the ophthalmology service via a referral from your GP.</p>
<p><a href="http://www.lancsteachinghospitals.nhs.uk/ophthalmology" target="_blank" title="Ophthalmology">Click here to view more information on the Lancashire Teaching Hospitals website.</a></p></div>
</div>
</div>
